      <p style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#9CA3AF;line-height:1.75;">The HPA axis does not care about your intentions. It responds to your actions. Thirty days of deliberate parasympathetic activation, disciplined sleep, and consistent supplementation will shift your cortisol-testosterone ratio in a direction your training can finally capitalize on. This is stewardship of what you have been given. Do not waste it by training hard in the wrong hormonal environment. The protocol is clear. Start tonight.</p>
